{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue la Corte}}}La Corte{\*\xmlclose} asegur\'f3: \'93(\'85)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\lang9226\langfe3082\langnp9226\insrsid6834625\charrsid465084 
